259
00:15:00,957 --> 00:15:03,383
but because I hope Your Majesty is able to weigh the goods and bads appropriately

260
00:15:03,383 --> 00:15:06,283
Postpone the reinstatement of Princess of Glory's power to handle the Harem's affairs

261
00:15:07,714 --> 00:15:09,896
